# Resources and Design System

## Strings
- Follow naming format: `[where].[section].[description]`.
- Default section is `content`.
- Group strings by screen/section and avoid reuse except shared dialogs.

## UI and design
- Build UI with existing Compose patterns.
- Reuse tokens/components from `core:design` for fonts, colors, typography, and theme.
- Keep visual behavior aligned with existing app patterns before adding new components.
